      ABC 6.0 6.0 6.0
      PERIODIC NONE
    &END CELL
    &COORD
 H     0.000000     0.000000     0.000000
 H     0.720000     0.000000     0.000000
    &END COORD
    &KIND H
      BASIS_SET DZVP-GTH-PADE
      POTENTIAL GTH-PADE-q1
    &END KIND
  &END SUBSYS
&END FORCE_EVAL
